        <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6">
            <h2 class="Value-category">E-sports</h2>
            <p class="Hobbies-text">I love all things about video games especially e-sports which has a close space to my heart. The games that I'm most invested into are Dota 2 and Leauge of Legends. One of my most memorable experiences was when I went to Seattle to watch The International in 2017 and lost my voice for cheering on my team.</p>
            <img src="/images/e-sports.jpg" class="Hobby-image">
        </div>
