            <h2 class="Value-category">Hiking</h2>
            <p class="Hobbies-text">Going to the outdoors and exploring nature through hiking is one of my favorite past times. I find that the best place for me to reflect about my life and my actions is in deep nature. It is through hiking where I can genuinely disconnect from all of my problems and ask myself about what really matters to me.</p>
            <img src="/images/outdoor-hobby.jpg" class="Hobby-image">
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6">
            <h2 class="Value-category">Reading</h2>
            <p class="Hobbies-text">I deeply cherish reading great books as I believe reading is the greatest medium for growing one's self. My favorite genre's are books in psychology and self-help. Some of my most beloved books are Quiet by Susan Cain, The Subtle Art of Not Giving a F*ck by Mark Manson, and Man's Search for meaning by Viktor Frankl.</p>
            <img src="/images/reading.jpg" class="Hobby-image">
        </div>
